The paper discusses the storage aspect of big data systems, which is closely related to database systems (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The comparison and analysis of different data models and file formats also falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also touches upon the communication between storage and processing technologies, which is relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
